text: "Möt mig i Gamla stan" () is a song written by Thomas G:son and Lina Eriksson, and performed by Magnus Carlsson at Melodifestivalen 2015, where the song ended up 9th in the final. ==Chart positions== {|class="wikitable plainrowheaders sortable" style="text-align:center;" |- !align="left"|Chart (2015) !align="center"|Peak position |- |} == References == Category:2015 singles Category:Magnus Carlsson songs Category:Melodifestivalen songs of 2015 Category:Songs about Stockholm Category:Songs written by Lina Eriksson Category:Songs written by Thomas G:son Category:Universal Music Group singles Category:2015 songs
